description: Use the Dash Member app to view and sign up for classes, teams, camps, events, and more, at facilities across the US and Canada. Search for programs to join, track your league standings, view upcoming events, RSVP for games, manage profiles for the whole family, make payments, and communicate with teammates using the Dash Member app.
